title: 3 more women come forward to accuse Cosby - Channel3000
text:
Three more women came forward publicly Wednesday to accuse Bill Cosby of sexually inappropriate behavior, creating yet another wave of allegations that the comedian abused his power by drugging and assaulting women. One woman was a cocktail server at a jazz club in Redondo Beach, California, in the 1970s.
